GIFTED GYPSY: Wandering mystic with a spontaneous psychic gift

The Gifted Gypsy is a wandering mystic and performer with a genuine
but unpredictable psychic gift. Unlike trained psionics, their
abilities manifest spontaneously and are tied to intuition rather than
discipline.

Gifted Gypsies choose from Rogue, Physical, Technical, and Lore skill
categories. They are culturally knowledgeable, persuasive, and
surprisingly perceptive. Their psychic gifts manifest as minor psionic
powers that expand with level.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: ME 12, MA 12.
  Equipment: Colorful travelling clothes, musical instrument or
    performance props, personal radio, a concealed knife, one week of
    rations, and a small cache of trade goods.

